          <h3>
           ‘63 Boycott broadcasts on PBS’ WORLD Channel
          </h3>
          <p>
           <a _mce_shape="rect" _mce_style="color: #000000;" shape="rect" style="font-family: Garamond, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;">
            '63 Boycott, a film
           </a>
           <span _mce_style="font-size: 10pt;" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Garamond, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 10pt;">
            by Rachel Dickson, Tracye A. Matthews, and Gordon Quinn, will make its world television broadcast premiere on PBS' World Channel
           </span>
           <a _mce_shape="rect" _mce_style="color: #000000;" shape="rect" style="font-family: Garamond, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;">
            February 25 at 9pm/8c
           </a>
           <span _mce_style="font-size: 10pt;" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Garamond, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 10pt;">
            , as part of the channel's LOCAL, USA series.
           </span>
          </p>
