         News &amp; Announcements
        </h3>
        <a class="news" href="https://csrpc.uchicago.edu/news/detail/faculty_spotlight_allyson_nadia_field">
         <h4>
          Faculty spotlight: Allyson Nadia Field
         </h4>
         <p>
          <span style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 'Gotham SSm A', 'Gotham SSm B', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.55555534362793px;">
           Allyson Nadia Field, an Associate Professor in the
          </span>
          <a href="https://cms.uchicago.edu/" style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); font-family: 'Gotham SSm A', 'Gotham SSm B', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.55555534362793px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;">
           Department of Cinema and Media Studies
          </a>
          <span style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 'Gotham SSm A', 'Gotham SSm B', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.55555534362793px;">
           and the College,
          </span>
          <span style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 'Gotham SSm A', 'Gotham SSm B', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.55555534362793px;">
           recently
          </span>
          <a href="https://news.uchicago.edu/story/silent-film-black-couples-kiss-discovered-added-national-film-registry" style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); font-family: 'Gotham SSm A', 'Gotham SSm B', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.55555534362793px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;">
           helped discover
          </a>
          <span style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: 'Gotham SSm A', 'Gotham SSm B', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.55555534362793px;">
           a silent film from 1898 that is thought to depict the earliest cinematic depiction of African-American affection.
          </span>
         </p>
         <p class="readmore">
          Read More
          <i class="icon-more">
          </i>
         </p>
        </a>
        <a class="news" href="https://csrpc.uchicago.edu/news/detail/alum_gordon_quinns_film_on_school_boycott_earns_oscar_buzz">
         <h4>
          Alum Gordon Quinn’s Film on School Boycott Earns Oscar Buzz
         </h4>
         <p>
          <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'ITC Garamond W01 Light', serif; font-size: 18px;">
           Gordon Quinn’s ’63 Boycott depicts historic city-wide walkout against school segregation.
          </span>
         </p>
         <p class="readmore">
          Read More
          <i class="icon-more">
          </i>
         </p>
